reviewText: I first saw this film when it aired on iBethel.TV where it was being shown in Redding, CA previously to the 2/14 release for churches around the world. It was amazing watching it and hearing the response of the Bethel Church audience.This film was of special interest to me because I am a substance abuse counselor and I'm always looking for material to show my clients to increase their faith in a God that love's them with love unimaginable. I eventually showed it to some of my clients who were blown away, encouraged and stretched by some of the stories on this film. It helped them to see that God's love transcends language, time, geographical location, and even through deep involvement with the occult.I highly recommend this film to anyone that needs to know that God loves them, no matter what!
